                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This can be observed by watching how much the row/key cache grows on each run.  I&apos;m not sure when this started or if it was always the case, but it&apos;s actually useful behavior when you want to benchmark just the cache, so it&apos;d be nice to preserve as an option.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
